"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"When someone issues instructions without an explanation, my mind goes ablaze.\\n\\n![Where I go to say no (Pride Day, 2014)](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fWHmqGwYUzwg_61OFi-Zd.JPG?height=3000&width=4000&size=large)\\n\\nHere are some examples:\\n\\nâ€œDesign this ad for meâ€ vs. â€Could we work on this together?â€\\n\\nâ€œPut your arms up for scannerâ€ vs. â€Please raise your armsâ€\\n\\nâ€If you do that, Iâ€™m outâ€ vs. â€This is really important to meâ€\\n\\nâ€Be here on timeâ€ vs. â€I will be here at this timeâ€”can you?â€\\n\\nâ€I was under the impressionâ€ vs. â€Here is my understandingâ€\\n\\nâ€Do that for me?â€ vs. â€It would mean a lot to me ifâ€\\n\\nWhen someone speaks to me this way, I absolutely cannot stand it. I have walked out of airports, left jobs, turned down lucrative acquisitions, and ended relationships instantly because of this.\\n\\nI refuse to be told. Please can you ask me?\\n\\nI will not comply. I want to know: why?\\n\\nI do not need you. Do you need me?\\n\\nI am independent. Are you?\\n\\nI have set my entire life up in a way so at any moment I can say: â€œNo.â€\\n\\nI am financially free for the rest of my future. Due to my wonderful parents, my past is free from pain. My present self is my gift to myself. My presence is mine.\\n\\nI am a time billonaire. You cannot rob me.\\n\\n![They asked me questions instead of giving me instructions](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3diO8QmDsMPwmG-k4lvYX.JPG?height=3024&width=4032)\\n\\nI wake up when I want. I work how I want. I do what I want. No one tells me what to do.\\n\\nEver.\\n\\nThat is who I am. If anyone *ever* tries to change that: they are gone.\\n\\nInstantly.\\n\\nIf you want to warm your hands on my flame, feel free.\\n\\nNever stick your hands in it.\\n\\nğŸ”¥\",\"timestamp\":1640097047,\"title\":\"Orders, Commands & Ultimatums ğŸ¥‹\",\"publication\":\"ricburton\"},\"digest\":\"uW6_fzFc8gH1QB3FefT-b2txKDx2eNqzWSlcR